metadata.name: Scylla
metadata.description:
Scylla is the fourth in our series Mythomemes, a collaboration between LIBESKIND ARTS and Burak Ta≈ü, bringing to life ancient mythological creatures, with original music composed by Fabio Fraschini. It is said that each mythical monster represents a fear of the human psyche. Scylla, threatening the straits of Messina along with her brother (and enemy) Charibdis, symbolizes hydrophobia or the fear of water.

The buyer of this NFT will also receive a higher quality 8K mp4 file.
